{"tid":1849603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼] 重要！懇求大家，口罩不儲多過三個月量","createTime":"2020-01-29T06:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T07:06:13.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"06a116b5ea82c88bcc23011f00e6231930d2204d","tid":1849603,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"from:作戰研究院 <br />\n<br />\n重要！懇求大家，口罩不儲多過三個月量<br />\n有三個月量儲備以上唔好再買住，海外網購唔計<br />\n<br />\n市面上有幾慘烈大家好清楚<br />\n基層朋友可能唔識網購唔識amazon<br />\n今日咁樣aboutthai咁樣真係好撚恐怖<br />\n留俾有需要人仕吧<br />\n點解我要無私讓俾人買?<br />\n抗疫唔係我戴左罩就無事，係全社區一齊戴<br />\n正如你見到有阿姐重洗重曬一樣<br />\n<br />\n有超過三個月口罩量，用良心價轉讓比其他市民啦🙏"},{"pid":"1581960cf59b6e7ab3ab925831ca85104b5b7fc2","tid":1849603,"uid":47208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:51:49.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n如果有三個月量, 就暫時唔好係本土途徑買口罩住"},{"pid":"1de3a7ad24a886ed68914883764a548ca5c3a576","tid":1849603,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"何栢良料港月需3億口罩 有私醫「一罩難求」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1849607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1849607</a>"},{"pid":"e0c046cd4224361eba89b6ccbd351bd43297c346","tid":1849603,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:56:50.000Z","msg":"香港人本性都係支那蝗蟲"},{"pid":"bc68ae1105f822a09be46296f6e769b131536ed9","tid":1849603,"uid":195169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:58:49.000Z","msg":"買嚟買去都買唔到...屋企得返半盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7852a547e8c4f4e6e50def7607090df9b127c019","tid":1849603,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjrMrcp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjrMrcp.jpg&h=e20e71f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇傳媒及出版嘅朋友